{"synckey":1647994723,"updated":[{"bookId":"37479811","bookmarkId":"37479811_7_1612-1719","chapterUid":7,"markText":"第一，有没有人能够成功地影响他人，甚至是影响比他们更有权势的人呢？第二，这些具备超强影响力的人们究竟掌握了怎样的影响力密码？","range":"1612-1719","createTime":1646796868,"type":1},{"bookId":"37479811","bookmarkId":"37479811_6_5213-5332","chapterUid":6,"markText":"书中讲解的逻辑是：首先，明确哪些场景是我们需要发挥影响力的重要工作场景；其次，针对重点场景，讲解对应的影响力整体思路和步骤，教大家应该怎么一步步做；最后，讲解每个步骤中具体用到哪些影响力工具以及怎么用，通过这个逻辑来帮助大家做到即学即用。","range":"5213-5332","createTime":1646700201,"type":1},{"bookId":"37479811","bookmarkId":"37479811_6_2468-2488","chapterUid":6,"markText":"第二，影响力是做好协作型工作的核心能力。","range":"2468-2488","createTime":1646700123,"type":1},{"bookId":"37479811","bookmarkId":"37479811_6_1303-1342","chapterUid":6,"markText":"独立型工作做得好只能让你在职场生存，协作型工作做得好才能让你加速发展。","range":"1303-1342","createTime":1646699298,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"开启篇 影响力三大密码","chapterUid":7,"chapterIdx":7},{"title":"第一部分 影响力——高潜人才的核心能力","chapterUid":6,"chapterIdx":6}],"book":{"bookId":"37479811","version":2133842296,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/54/YueWen_37479811/s_YueWen_37479811.jpg","title":"影响力密码：打开协作中的锁","author":"王明伟","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KD9IP$iYt8^vo~j]IBogM{","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#091d35"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#001c41"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#001c4d"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#20314b"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#0d3158"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#003165"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#354864"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#274971"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#0d497e"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#004998"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#446189"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#1762a3"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#50617b"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#3d7cbd"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#6a7b94"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#517cb0"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#8495ad"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#7895bc"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#6c96ca"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#4097e8"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#84b1e5"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#72b1f6"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#57b2ff"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#b6cae2"},{"key":"8/6","hex":